highlights.text: Perunggu has the most spots on Viral Songs Indonesia. “Aku Ada Untukmu” is the highest at #20.
“Cantik Tapi Bau” by Sukses Lancar Rejeki is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Indonesia at #28.
“About You” by The 1975 has been on Viral Songs Indonesia the longest, at 389 days straight.
“PRODUK TIMUR” by S KEI ENT, KAPTEN HIPHOP, and Jacson Zeran is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Indonesia, up 14 spots at #78.
